pg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Toby-Jones-Alan-Bates@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Toby-Jones-Alan-Bates@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Toby-Jones-Alan-Bates@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Toby-Jones-Alan-Bates@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>演员托比·琼斯表示艾伦·贝茨拒绝了<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024">2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节</a>开幕的邀请。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-set-times-stage-splits-3749871"><b>格拉斯顿伯里音乐节 2024：查看迄今为止的完整阵容和舞台划分</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>英国独立电视台热播连续剧<em>《贝茨先生大战邮局》</em>中饰演这位前副局长的演员透露，领导对抗邮局的前副局长有机会担任今年值得农场节的开幕嘉宾。</p><p>该剧根据正在发生的真实故事改编，众多副邮政局长面临盗窃、欺诈和虚假会计的指控，而问题的真正根源是 IT 系统缺陷造成的。</p><p>据琼斯称，该提议已提交给贝茨，但他立即拒绝了该提议，因为他无意成为名人。</p><p> “在这种文化中，他似乎不像我们一样受到同样的力量的影响。他是买不到的，”这位演员在海伊音乐节上对观众说（来自<a href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2024/06/02/alan-bates-cant-be-bought-toby-jones-glastonbury/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《电讯报</em></a>》）。 “他被要求开设格拉斯顿伯里音乐节。 &#39;不，谢谢。&#39;他被要求做这些事情，但他不想做任何事情。他说，‘我有工作要做’，那就是把这些事情完成。”</p><p>他继续说道，并对贝茨也拒绝了大英帝国勋章表示认可。 “他是一位英雄，在完成任务之前他不想要任何荣誉。 </p><figure id="attachment_3761927" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3761927" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-3761927 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Toby-Jones@2000x1270.jpg" alt="托比·琼斯 (Toby Jones) 出席卢卡斯影业 (Lucas Films) 影片《夺宝奇兵：夺宝奇兵》(Indiana Jones and the Dial of Destiny) 洛杉矶首映式" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Toby-Jones@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Toby-Jones@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Toby-Jones@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Toby-Jones@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Toby-Jones@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Toby-Jones@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3761927" class="wp-caption-text">托比·琼斯 (Toby Jones) 出席卢卡斯影业 (Lucas Films) 影片《夺宝奇兵：夺宝奇兵》(Indiana Jones and the Dial of Destiny) 的洛杉矶首映式。图片来源：Axelle/Bauer-Griffin/FilmMagic/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> “我不会说这些价值观是我成长过程中所伴随的，但我记得有人对我说教——关于责任和坚持到底——这些是非常非常不时尚的事情，可能与我们的价值观形成鲜明对比。已经在政府部门生活了一段时间了。”</p><p>格拉斯顿伯里音乐节过去曾因历史人物的开幕而闻名，其中包括大卫·阿滕伯勒爵士和前工党领袖杰里米·科尔宾。</p><p>标志性的沃西农场音乐节将于今年 6 月 26 日至 30 日举行，组织者于 4 月份分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-revealed-who-playing-poster-3600775https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-revealed-who-playing-poster-3600775">2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的官方阵容</a>。在最初的公告中，已确认<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">酷玩乐队 (Coldplay)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a>将在今年夏天的标志性金字塔舞台上领衔主演，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shania-twain">仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain)</a>将在周日的传奇时段表演。</p><p>自此之后，组织者开始倒计时今年的活动，并逐渐公布在现场其他舞台上表演的艺术家。这是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-adds-more-names-to-line-up-acoustic-stage-3616963">新艺术家的消息开始的，这是新艺术家将成为声学舞台的头条</a>新闻，随后是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/caity-baser-lulu-frank-turner-and-skindred-among-new-names-for-glastonbury-2024-line-up-in-field-of-avalon-reveal-3618404">加入Avalon阵容</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-english-teacher-sprints-bob-vylan-and-lottery-winners-among-acts-for-left-field-line-up-3752348">左场</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-announce-stacked-line-up-for-woodsies-area-3752059">木材</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/faithless-fatboy-slim-camelphat-groove-armada-lead-glastonbury-2024-glade-area-line-up-3749471">GLADES</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-romy-kelly-lee-owens-shygirl-and-more-added-to-glastonbury-as-silver-hayes-line-up-revealed-3751900">Silver Hayes</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-announces-full-line-up-for-the-park-including-two-new-venues-3756495">The Park，Park</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-festival-announces-2024-line-up-for-the-common-3753302">The Common，Common</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-confidence-man-bicep-lead-block9-lineup-genosys-to-return-3759260">Block9</a>和Block9和更多的。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4fLcwiNTQ7/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076